CTetris:

    "CTetris" stands for C of Teteris

Docs:
    * http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/tetris

Program:
    * binary file name: #1
    * program name: #1

Language:
    * c

Library/API:
    * ISO C99
    * GNU C Library
    * ncurses

Build System:
    * GNU Make

Naming Convention:
    Num(#)  Lowercase   Capitalization  Uppercase
    1       ctetris     CTetris         CTETRIS 
    2       ct          CT              CT
